title: 109: Pilot Pete’s Premiere (Part 1)
itunes:title: 109: Pilot Pete’s Premiere (Part 1)
description:
The Broads dive into the first HALF of Pete Weber’s first Bachelor episode! This 3 hour episode had some much to chat about The Broads decided to break it into two episodes (part two will be released tomorrow 1/7). Join as they discuss the limo entrances, the first rose ceremony, see if their cast bio episode guesses were correct, laugh their asses off, and gear up for this sure to be DRAMA filled season! 
***Note: Jess got it wrong and Eunice did go home the first night - bye to all the flight attendants:(
Follow along as Pete’s season continues by subscribing to the podcast!
